===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|ls=ic|子|𠀠|廾|t1=child|t2=basket|t3=two hands}} - throwing out a child in a basket. {{lang|zh|子}} was often inverted as {{lang|zh|𠫓}}.

In the oracle bone script form, {{lang|zh|子}} may appear with dots on either side of its head and body, perhaps representing amniotic fluid or dust.

